n我: 係呀&hellip;順便搭吓部lift咁囉...<br />\n(屌 一講完都覺自己好撚on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 想搵窿捐 不過佢居然照應<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<br />\n女: 喔&hellip;部lift都OK架 都好快<br />\n(我哋兩個各自都已經開始陰陰嘴笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<br />\n我: 係... 部lift真係唔話得 每次都好安全咁送我哋去到目的地<br />\n女: 係呀 仲要好穩定 搭得好舒服 唔會暈浪<br />\n<br />\n我: 差唔多到喇喎 我去上堂喇 你呢?<br />\n女: (笑) 吓 我搭完lift囉 咁一齊去上堂啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後就熟絡咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 識咗呢個fd 都幾年喇 到依家每次見親面 都成日會案件重演 大家又再鳩噏派膠 約食飯一坐低就會 咦食飯呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一齊搭車一上車就 咦搭車呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咦XX呀 咦XX呀 然後開始後面啲濕鳩對話 得我哋兩個明白點解要笑 其它人唔知發生咩嘢事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nhi bye fd 多謝你陪咗我咁耐呀 多謝你陪我鳩噏足咁多年 多謝部lift令我哋可以陪住對方咁多高山低谷 多謝你體諒同接受我表面鳩噏之下既另一面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我哋都係對方特別的存在 朋友就係想大家睇住對方幸福快樂 好快有日 我就可以對你講<br />\n&lsquo;咦 結婚呀?&rsquo; <br />\n&lsquo;係呀&hellip;你呢?&rsquo;<br />\n&lsquo;冇呀 嚟酒店搭吓部lift咁囉&rsquo;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你要幸福呀 知道嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T05:42:27.000Z","msg":"咁多人搭lift相識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T06:19:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20b77ce8cb2ac8fc92d1621b10fc748d7f7000da","tid":2486734,"uid":393145,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"a890851a4354bbaa45d403516e65ea016c2e0303","tid":2486734,"uid":109050,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T06:12:29.000Z","msg":"呢D鳩UP都肯同你吹